Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:26.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}与你一起极限战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:29.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}狰狞无比的凄惨之战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}爱总是无法无天的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:34.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}仅属于我的放荡之战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:38.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那句再见  无法说出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:41.12,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:43.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我不明白  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:46.00,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}搞不明白自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:51.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这份心情无法释怀  无法割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:56.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}越是想着不可以  就陷得越深
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:01.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}变得连自己都开始怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:05.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不如相信它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:09.59,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不管会失去什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:12.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都决定要伴随在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:13.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:16.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:18.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就算到了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:21.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:23.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}命运要我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:26.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:29.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}要我止步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:31.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:33.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这理由却还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:38.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我可为你抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:39.24,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}喂
